  "merger_description": "Symal Group Limited (**Symal Group****)** is proposing to acquire Shamrock Equipment Pty Ltd, Shamrock Civil Engineering Pty Ltd Shamrock Group and Phoenix Investments Queensland Pty Ltd and certain assets including plant and equipment (together,\u00a0**Shamrock Group**) (the\u00a0**Acquisition**).\n\nSymal Group is a civil construction and engineering services provider across the roads, rail, defence, ports and energy sectors, including demolition, bulk earthworks, site preparation, haulage and tip operations services. Symal Group operates businesses under the Symal, Sycle, Unyte, Searo and Wamarra brands.\n\nShamrock Group is a civil construction, equipment and engineering services provider across the roads, defence, resources, landfill, public infrastructure, and water and gas sectors, including earthworks, demolition and decontamination services.",
